@base = http://localhost:8000/api

### Get full streak data (includes score streak, decay strength, freeze tokens, partner)
GET {{base}}/streaks

### Use a freeze token to protect streak on a missed day
POST {{base}}/streaks/freeze

### Invite a partner by email
POST {{base}}/streaks/partner/invite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "friend@example.com"
}

### Accept a partner invite by token
POST {{base}}/streaks/partner/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "INVITE_TOKEN_UUID"
}

### Remove active partner streak
DELETE {{base}}/streaks/partner
